	(text "Rpullmin = (Vcc - VOLmax) / IOLmax\nRpullmin = (3.3V - 0.2V) / 0.004 A\nRpullmin = 775 ohms\n\nRpullmax = tr / (0.8473 * Cb)\nRpullmax = 300us / (0.8473 * 100pF)\nRpullmax = 3540\n\nCb chosen off realistic bus capacitance. This design would be nowhere\nnear the datasheets' max capacitance of 400pF for 400kHz fast mode I2C."
